Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的名字叫奥利弗・奎恩\NMy name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}五年里  我被困在地狱一般的小岛上\NAfter five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我回来只有一个目标\NI have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拯救我的城市\Nto save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但要达到目标  我不能像过去一样成为凶手\NBut to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了纪念我的朋友\NTo honor my friend's memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只能伪装成另一个人\NI must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}深切怀念托马斯・梅林\N孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}成为另一个存在\NI must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}《绿箭》前情回顾\NPreviously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}根据15号刑事诉讼程序\NWe would like to serve notice to the defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想要向被告宣布\Npursuant to rule of criminal procedure 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望能在你提出死刑前\NI would like to have a conversation with you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和你进行一次谈话\Nbefore you seek the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莫伊拉  你隐瞒了什么\NMoira, what don't I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些事情\NThere are some things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}永远不能提起\Nthat must never be spoken of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我输给他两次了  我不知道怎么阻止他\NHe's beaten me twice, and I don't know how to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是谁\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你一旦知道了  你的生活就要变样了\NOnce you know, your life will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}六年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊  爸爸  大学很棒\NYeah, dad, college is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  我和我的新室友很合得来\NNo, me and my new roommate totally hit it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们是闺蜜\NWe're like besties.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  爸爸  我得回化学实验室了\NOk. Yeah, dad, I got to get back to chem lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊  看来今晚的确很漫长\NYes. It looks like I got a long night ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉  挂断电话\NSara. Get off the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  爱你  老爸  再见\NOk. Love you, dad. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奥利\NOllie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真麻烦\NYou are trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兰斯警探怎么样\NHow is Detective Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他和往常一样  毫无头绪\NAh, he's clueless, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我好渴啊\NGuess I was thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你听到了吗\NDid you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}1  2  3\N1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}越来越近了\NIt's getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这么说可不太科学\NThat's not very scientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还懂科学呀\NAnd what would you know about science,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}常春藤联盟辍学先生\NMr. Ivy League drop out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我碰巧很了解科学\NI happen to know a lot about science.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道  发酵\NI know... fermentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我懂  生物\NI know...biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}劳蕾尔会宰了我的\NLaurel's gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她真的会宰了我的\NOh, she's so gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你姐姐不会知道的\NYour sister will never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来吧\NJust come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这雷真够近的\NOk, that one was really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会没事的\NWe're going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奥利弗\NOliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救命  救命\NHelp! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奥利弗\NOliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}睡不着吗\NCan't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不喜欢闭上眼睛\NI don't do well with my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你让我住在这\NHey, thanks for letting me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你在为你妈妈的事烦心\NI know you got a lot going on with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西娅大部分时间住在她男友家  所以...\NThea's mostly staying at her boyfriend's. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别担心有人会发现你回来了\Ndon't worry about anyone finding out that you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你理解\NThanks for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不理解\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的家人每一天都在想你\NYou know, not a day goes by that your family doesn't miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吗  你怎么知道的\NYeah? How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我就想你\NBecause I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得他们不会像你这么高兴见到我的\NI don't think they'll be as happy to see me as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你怎么可以那样说\NHow can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道当你离家很久时\NI know how hard it is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}要再回家是很困难的\Nto come home when you've been gone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我猜我爸爸和劳蕾尔\NI'm guessing my father and Laurel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可不怎么高兴见到你\Nweren't too happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一开始不高兴\NNo. No, not at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道你和她复合没有\NI wasn't sure if you and she ever got back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们试过\NWe tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}太难以承受了\NIt's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想有些事最好还是留在过去\NI guess some things, you know, it's better left in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不等奎恩先生了  我们开始吧\NI'm done waiting for Mr. Queen. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉我迟到了\NSorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有个老朋友来了城里\NThere's an old friend... in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我刚向你母亲和妹妹解释完\NI just finished explaining to your mother and sister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兰斯小姐是检方的第二律师\Nthat Miss Lance will be sitting second chair for the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这有利益冲突\NThis is a conflict of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兰斯小姐基本是在奎恩家长大的\NMiss Lance practically grew up in the Queen house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得你这是在夸大事实\NI think you're overstating matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等我把冲突人兰斯小姐移出这起案子再看吧\NOh, we'll see when I move to conflict Miss Lance off this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许这很快就不是一起案子了\NMaybe there won't be a case much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来这里不只是为了陪兰斯小姐\NI come here not just with Miss Lance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还带来了有条件认罪建议\Nbut also with a plea offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}终身监禁  可能保释\NLife, with the possibility of parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不认罪  奎恩女士是无辜的\NWe are not pleading out. Mrs. Queen is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她教唆了503起杀人案\NShe aided and abetted 503 homicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是在一个名叫马尔科姆・梅林的\NUnder duress from a homicidal maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杀人狂的强迫下做的\Nnamed Malcolm Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她还在犯罪阴谋执行之前\NShe also withdrew from the criminal conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-抽身而退  -就早了五分钟\N- prior to its execution. - Five minutes prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马尔科姆・梅林死了  陪审团\NWith Malcolm Merlyn dead, a jury's going
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总要找到个替罪羊\Nto want to have to blame someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果她不接受这笔交易\NIf she doesn't take the deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那她就可能被判处死刑\Nthen she's facing the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听起来很像敲诈\NSounds a lot like blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是现实  还有更多...\NTry reality. And here's some more--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们得到你最近十年的手机短信\NWe've subpoenaed over a decades' worth of phone messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}电话记录  信件和邮件\Nphone records, letters and emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我敢肯定我找到了一些信息\NI'm willing to bet I find
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能把你"受到强迫"的辩词驳得体无完肤\Nsomething that crushes your duress defense to powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}唐纳先生\NMr. Donner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你不介意的话\Nif you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想要几天时间来考虑你的提议\NI'd like a few days to consider your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然可以\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先失陪了\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我马上回来\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}劳蕾尔\NLaurel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}车里见\NI'll meet you at the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要起诉我妈妈吗\NYou're prosecuting my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这案子不是我要求的  而是分配给我的\NI didn't ask for this case. I was assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-那就拒绝啊  -这是份新工作  奥利弗\N- So say no! - It's a new job, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没多大影响力  我仅有的影响力\NI don't have a lot of pull. And what pull I do have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也都用来帮你母亲搞那个认罪协议了\NI used to get that plea bargain for your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是你的主意吗\NThis was your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}终身监禁\NLife in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}地方检察官对死刑的事是认真的  奥利\NThe D.A. is serious about the death penalty, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都知道失去一个人的感觉\NWe both know what it's like to lose someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好好想想  救救你妈的命\NSo think about it and save your mother's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还好吗\NAre you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许上周我没说清楚\NIn case I wasn't clear last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想再回答那个问题了\NI'm done answering that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救命\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救命\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这边\NOver here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没事吧\NYou OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你妈妈的事情进展怎么样了\NHow did everything go with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我遇到你姐姐了  她在负责这个案子\NI ran into your sister. She's working on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你没告诉她...  -没有\N- You didn't tell her... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我理解为什么有时要保守秘密\NI know a little something about keeping secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也尊重这些秘密  尽管我...\Nand respecting them, even though I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}完全不明白为什么你要保守秘密\Ntotally understand why you're keeping yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是不是\NIs this--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是不是因为岛上发生的事\NIs it because of what happened on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是后来的事\NAfter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我做了一些事\NThere were things that I did;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为了生存不得不做的事\Nthings that I had to do to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无法原谅的事\NThings that there's no forgiveness for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说到原谅的话\NWell, that's the thing about forgiveness--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不请求原谅怎么得到原谅呢\Nyou can't get it until you ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}梅林\NMerlyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是什么人\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只是个武士  跟你一样\NJust a warrior. Like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么穿得跟马尔科姆・梅林一样\NWhy are you dressed like Malcolm Merlyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁派你来的\NHuh? Who sent you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还记得第一次看见这件兜帽服的时候\NI remember the first time I saw this hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}穿在莎朵的身上\NShado was wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些就是你的装备总部了吧\NThis is quite the set-up that you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你就在这里为了星城孤军奋战的\NWhere you're launching your one man war for Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不是孤军奋战\NI'm not one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我的朋友\NThese are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}约翰・狄格尔和费利西蒂・斯莫克\NThis is John Diggle and Felicity Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计们  这是莎拉\NGuys. This is Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}欢迎回家  莎拉\NWelcome home, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听到你没死的消息时我很高兴\NI was happy to hear you're not dead anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说  你第一次没死之前我不认识你\NI mean, I didn't know you before you didn't die the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很高兴你还活着\NI'm still glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们刚刚在奎恩宅邸遇到一个不速之客\NWe just had an uninvited guest in the Queen mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}受过训练  武艺高超\NTrained. Highly skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且他穿的跟梅林一样\NAnd he was dressed like Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我上次确认过  马尔科姆・梅林已经死亡\NWell, the last I checked Malcolm Merlyn was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一支利箭刺穿了他的心脏\Ncourtesy of an arrow jammed through his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是他  那是个追随者\NIt wasn't him. It was a follower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个决心报复的下属  不管是什么人\Nan underling bent on revenge. Whoever it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他知道我是谁\NHe knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天  我可没给过你一袋土\NGee, I didn't get you a bag of dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在宅子里发现的  山寨梅林带进来的\NI found it in the house. Copycat Merlyn tracked it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你分析一下  希望能够帮我找到他\NI want you to analyze it. Hopefully it'll lead me right to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后呢\NThen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果这个冒牌货那么想追随马尔科姆・梅林\NIf this pretender wants to follow Malcolm Merlyn so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就追随他一起进坟墓吧\Nhe can follow him right into a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉  我们会找到这家伙的\NSara? We'll find this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想让你那么做\NI don't want you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不是来找你的  奥利\NHe wasn't after you, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是来找我的\NHe's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是什么人\NWho is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他被称作阿奥阿  "第一个"\NHe's called Al Qw-Al, "The First".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是刺客联盟的成员\NAnd he's a member of the League of Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等  刺客联盟\NWait. Wait. The League of Assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还以为是虚构的呢\NI thought they were a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刺客联盟是什么  拜托\NWhat's the League of Assassins? And please,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可别告诉我就是刺客组成的联盟\Ndon't say it's a league made up of assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  这是个都市传奇\NNo, it's an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从阿富汗一个部落首领那里听说的\NI heard about them in afghanistan from a tribal leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他号称有一个古老的刺客宗派\NHe claimed there was an ancient sect of assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杀人如魔鬼  行踪似魑魅\Ndeadly warriors that killed and vanished like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还以为他是抽嗨了不清醒才这么说的\NThought he was smoking what he was selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想告诉你的  奥利  但你不听\NI tried to tell you, Ollie, but you wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就是你过去四年待的地方\NThat's where you've been the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你学会战斗的地方\NThat's where you learned to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是他们的一员\NYou're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}翻船之后  联盟一个成员救了我\NAfter the freighter, a member of the league rescued me;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让我入伙并把我带去了南达尔巴特\Ntook me in and brought me to Nanda Parbatt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们把我改造成了现在的样子\NThey remade me into what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我发誓对他们效忠\NAnd I swore them my allegiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那他们现在为什么翻箱倒柜想把你找出来\NWhy are they kicking down doors trying to find you now?
