Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论如何  你得跟我们回去\NRegardless, you're coming back with us.
