Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和你一样  我也不是一个人\NLike you, I did not come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你不自愿回去\NIf you will not return willingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会毁了你的家人\Nwe'll stay to bury your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你一点都没哆嗦\NYou're not even flinching when he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几年前我就不怕疼了\NPain and I came to a little understanding few years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好了\NDone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刺客联盟\NThe league of assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她为什么不告诉我这些年发生了什么\NWhy wouldn't she tell me what happened to her all those years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许和你不告诉我们\NProbably the same reason why you didn't tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在岛上遇到过什么的理由一样\Nwhat happened to you on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们要保护兰斯一家人\NWe need to protect the Lances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来保护劳蕾尔\NI'll take Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我呢\NWhat can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么都不做  你受伤了  就在这里待着\NNothing. You're hurt, and you need to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我爸怎么办\NWhat about my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会和兰斯警探谈的\NI'll go talk to Detective Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让他离开这里几天\NTell him he needs to get out town for a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}请不要告诉他我的事\NPlease don't tell him about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我能保密  问他就知道了\NI can keep a secret. Just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们三人的队伍可真好\NYou three are quite the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们经历过一些事\NWe have our moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起来\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别  不要  求你们了\NWait, wait, no, no, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}求你们了  不要\NPlease, please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你越挣扎\NThe more you struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就越痛\Nthe more it'll hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别这样  求你们了\NNo, no, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}求你们了\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}住手\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放开她\NLet her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你没资格命令我\NYou don't give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没资格  但船长有\NNo, that would be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他现在听我指令行事\NBut he works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是吧\NDoesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}救救我  求你了\NHelp me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}劳蕾尔  还是你老爸  听我说\NLaurel, listen, it's your father--again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道自从上周我让你停车\NOk, now listen, I know you're still mad at me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对你说了那番话之后你还在生我气\Nafter what I said when you got pulled over last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我们这样冷战是不对的\Nbut it's not right, us not talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以拜托你回我电话好吗\NSo please, just-- just call me, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兰斯警探  我知道你已经下班\NDetective Lance! I knew you'd be getting home around now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在应该准备回家\Nbecause your shift has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我黑了你的手机\NWhich I knew because I kind of pinged your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}斯莫克小姐\NMiss Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的工作给你带来了蟑螂[危机]\NYou have cockroaches and they mean business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你什么时候开始上门服务的\NSince when did you start making house calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为你有危险\NSince you're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不怕蟑螂\NI'm not afraid of cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在真的很危险\NYes, you're in real danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得离开星城几天\NYou need to get out of town for a couple days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一换上警服  就要面对危险\NListen, I'm in danger every time I put on this uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你最好说得具体点\Nso you're going to have to be a little more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有个叫做刺客联盟的组织\NThere's an organization called the League of Assassins
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}里面有三个成员要对付你\Nand three of its members are targeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说出来感觉有点莫名其妙\NIt...sounded a little less crazy in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不信\NI doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}马尔科姆・梅林就是其中一员\NMalcolm Merlyn was apparently a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这样说  你大概能明白\NThat should give you some sort of idea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们要面对的是什么角色了吧\Nabout the type of people we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  我相信你\NOk, I'll bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我究竟怎么惹到他们了\NWhat did I do to piss them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个嘛\NThat...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}说来话长\Nis a really long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你只要  只要相信我就好\NYou just... you need to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你待在星城很不安全\NYou're not safe here in starling city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}斯莫克  在这里谁能安全呢\NSmoak, nobody's safe, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}警察就更不可能了\NEspecially not us cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干的就是挨枪子的活儿\NWe get shot at for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而我今天的活儿  刚结束\NAnd my shift? It just ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-兰斯警探  -晚安\N- Detective Lance! - Good-night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等等  你得听我说啊\NWait, you need to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}晚安  斯莫克小姐\NGood night, Miss Smoak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这么说  你是不打算离开这里了\NSo I guess this means you're not leaving town?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}晚上好\NEvening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我该早点告诉你的\NI should have said this earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们俩不太适合\Nbut it's not appropriate for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谈论你妈妈的案件\Nto be discussing your mother's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是刚好在附近\NActually, I was in the neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我想或许可以过来\Nso I thought that I would swing by
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看你要不要一起吃个饭\Nand see if I could give you a ride home and maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我再送你回家\Nget a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我今天很累了  我不想再听你\NIt's been a long day. I don't need an even longer night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}长篇大论说服我别插手你母亲的案件\Nof you trying to talk me out of your mother's plea agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}劳蕾尔\NLaurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我保证  这和我母亲的案子无关\NI promise, this has nothing to do with my mother's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你这几周过得很辛苦\NYou've had a rough couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.23,0:23:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定不需要找个朋友陪陪\NYou really going to tell me you couldn't use a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}走吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-情况如何  -很糟糕\N- How'd it go? - Badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他要么不相信我  要么以为我开玩笑\NHe either didn't believe me or didn't take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在想想  我或许不该提到\NIn hindsight, I probably shouldn't have led
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}刺客联盟\Nwith League of Assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在怎么办\NWhat do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要干什么  奥利弗叫你待在这\NWhat are you doing? Oliver told you to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不是不希望你父亲知道你还活着么\NI thought you didn't want your father to know you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}确实  但告诉他总比害死他好\NI don't. But it's better than him not being.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-你又打算去哪儿  -跟你一起走\N- Where do you think you're going? - With you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可不能让你孤身冒险\NI'm not going to let you go out there without any back-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狄格  虽然你是经验丰富的特种兵\NDig, you may be a three tour special forces veteran,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但跟我所受过的训练相比\Nbut I was trained by the people that make the special forces
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就是大巫见小巫了  让开\Nlook like a kindergarten class. So step aside
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}否则别怪我不客气\Nor get put down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你这是去送死  莎拉\NIt's your funeral, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}已经死过一回了\NIt wouldn't be my first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.01,0:25:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  这不可能\NNo, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.73,0:25:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不可能是莎拉\NIt can't be Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.21,0:25:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是我  是莎拉\NIt's me. It's Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.55,0:25:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}爸爸\NDaddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.90,0:25:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事了\NIt's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.84,0:25:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.22,0:25:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.25,0:25:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是你的茶  请问你还需要什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.38,0:25:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不用了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会说中文了\NYou speak Chinese now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.09,0:25:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这几年来学了不少东西\NPicked up a couple things in the past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.86,0:25:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么不告诉我们  你还活着\NWhy didn't you let us know that you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.42,0:26:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我和你妈妈  我们...\NI mean, your mother and I, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都很想念你\NWe missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.26,0:26:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你姐姐也是\NAnd your sister did, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.43,0:26:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道的吧\NYou know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.38,0:26:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你们离婚了\NI know you got divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.87,0:26:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但这不是你的错\NBut it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.41,0:26:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是我的问题\NThat was on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问题因我而起\NBecause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.59,0:26:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没关系  一切都无关紧要  知道吗\NIt's all right. None of that matters now. You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.21,0:26:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为你回家了  宝贝  你回家了\N'cause you're home, sweetie, you're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.56,0:26:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有麻烦了吗\NAre you in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.04,0:26:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  爸爸\NNo, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是你有麻烦了\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.49,0:26:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是你让费利西蒂・斯莫克劝我离开星城的\NYou sent Felicity Smoak to warn me to leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.71,0:27:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你认识绿箭侠\NYou know the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.22,0:27:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是那个蒙面女\NYou're the girl in the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.41,0:27:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你一直在贫民区锄强扶弱\NYou've been kicking the crap out of creeps in the glades.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.49,0:27:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你已经回来好几周了\NYou've been home for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.60,0:27:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我\NTell me something--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果这些杀手  没有现身\NIf these assassins, if they hadn't shown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是不是永远不会让我们知道你还活着\Nwould you have ever let us know that you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.81,0:27:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.35,0:27:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}费利西蒂说那些人是某个联盟的成员\NFelicity said that these guys were part of a league of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们想干什么\NWhat do they want with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.00,0:27:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟所有刺客一样  想干掉他们的目标\NWhat all assassins want-- to terminate their objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.74,0:27:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真是荒谬\NOh, this is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.50,0:27:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}父亲  我们该走了\NDad, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.09,0:27:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  我们哪里都不去\NNo, we are not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.53,0:27:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你坐下来详细地告诉我\NNot until you sit down and you tell me exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.23,0:27:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你到底惹上了什么事\Nwhat you've gotten yourself into.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.47,0:27:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是个出色的警察  而且你很坚强\NYou are an amazing cop and you are strong
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很正派  很诚实\Nand decent and honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.39,0:27:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但这些人  他们能够\NBut these men, they will
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.28,0:28:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不费吹灰之力就把你干掉\Ncut you down before you can lift a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.50,0:28:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}求你了  跟我一起走吧\NNow please. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}虽然挺破的  但是...\NI'm afraid it's not much, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.43,0:28:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也算是个家\NIt's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.55,0:28:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么你要把门锁起来\NWhy did you lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.10,0:28:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  不是那个意思\NNo, no, no, no. It's not because...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.05,0:28:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}习惯而已  这里的船员们不是很友好\NIt's just a habit. My shipmates aren't exactly the nicest bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.44,0:28:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}请进来吧  随便坐\NPlease, come in. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.48,0:29:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我叫艾沃\NMy name is Ivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安东尼・艾沃博士\NDr. Anthony Ivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.95,0:29:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你的名字是\NAnd you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.73,0:29:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉\NSara.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.35,0:29:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很高兴见到你  莎拉\NNice to meet you, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.06,0:29:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么把那些人锁在笼子里\NWhy do you keep those people down there in those cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.81,0:29:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是我的工作  我需要他们\NIt's my work. I need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.30,0:29:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么工作\NWhat work?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.50,0:29:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要拯救人类  莎拉\NI am going to save the human race, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.64,0:29:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许你能帮助我\NMaybe you can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.35,0:29:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我注意到你吃饭的时候没有喝酒\NI noticed you didn't have a drink at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.08,0:29:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  我没喝\NNo. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.68,0:29:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在愿不愿意承认  上周你以为我\NSo will you now admit that you and my father
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.13,0:29:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}又开始酗酒\Noverreacted last week
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.44,0:29:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你和我父亲的反应有点过激了\Nwhen you thought that I was becoming a drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.77,0:29:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我愿意承认我关心你\NI am prepared to admit that I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.01,0:30:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以你才坚持要送我到房间门口吗\NIs that why you insisted on walking me to my door?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真懂我\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.27,0:30:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是想确保你的安全\NI just wanted to make sure you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.36,0:30:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样才安全\NThis is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.38,0:30:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个\NThis...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.82,0:30:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们不能这么做\NWe shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你为什么要陪着我走这么久\NThen why did you come all the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.23,0:30:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很抱歉  我让你误会了我的意思\NI'm really sorry if I was sending the wrong message.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.32,0:30:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.47,0:30:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  我知道你的意思\NNo, no, I got the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我每天都很清楚你的意思\NI get it loud and clear every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快跑\NRun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.23,0:30:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}快跑  远离劳蕾尔\NRun, run away from Laurel,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.89,0:30:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}越快越好\Nrun as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.70,0:30:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-劳蕾尔  别这样  -莎拉\N- Laurel, come on.  - Sara...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.85,0:30:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她和你一起上了"金牌奎恩号"\NShe got on "The gambit" With you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.21,0:30:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我父亲  他\NMy father, he--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.39,0:30:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他躲进酒瓶里醉生梦死\NHe climbed into a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.16,0:30:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我母亲  她  她躲进车里\NMy mother, she--she climbed into her car
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.25,0:30:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}驶离了这个家  然后是汤米...\Nand she drove away, and then Tommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.44,0:30:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我做了什么  为什么所有人都要离开\NWhat is so wrong with me that everybody leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.29,0:31:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我永远不会离开你\NI will never leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.45,0:31:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会离开的\NUntil you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.54,0:31:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得我锁了门\NI thought I locked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.18,0:31:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}待在这里\NStay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奥利\NOllie?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.43,0:31:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有什么状况吗\NAnything?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.65,0:31:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一切正常\NAll good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.53,0:31:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我得走了\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.04,0:31:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  刚才说的话我很抱歉\NListen, I'm sorry about what I said--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.02,0:31:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不用道歉\NDon't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.42,0:31:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}待在这里别出去\NJust stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.92,0:32:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}费利西蒂  阿奥阿来劳蕾尔的住处了\NFelicity, Al Ow-al was at laurel's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.22,0:32:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么  她没事吧\NWhat? Is she ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.30,0:32:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她没事  看来他在我们到达之前离开了\NShe's fine. Looks like he moved out before we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.78,0:32:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是如果劳蕾尔不是他的目标\NBut if Laurel's not his target...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.93,0:32:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的目标是兰斯  我需要他的地址\NHe's after Lance, and I need a location now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.25,0:32:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我居然没想到应该来这里找你\NWell, I can't believe I didn't think to look for you up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.95,0:32:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里的视野很好  能看到整个城市\NIt's a good vantage point. You can see the whole city.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.54,0:32:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就像站在电线上的鸟\NLike a bird on a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.28,0:32:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我之前在的地方  要选择一个新名字\NWhere I was, they have you choose a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.84,0:32:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我选的是塔尔・莎菲尔\NI chose Ta-er Sah-fer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.29,0:32:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是一个阿拉伯名字\NIt's Arabic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.03,0:32:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}意思是金丝雀\NFor canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.10,0:32:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你十岁的时候我给你买了那只金丝雀\NI bought you that canary when you were ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.41,0:32:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我离家非常远\NI was as far from home as you can get,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.77,0:32:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我从未忘记家在哪里\Nbut I never forgot where I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:32:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人说  忘记一个人\NYou know how they say the first thing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.98,0:33:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最先忘记的是他的声音\Nyou forget about somebody when they're gone is their voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.76,0:33:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}记得他们的脸\NYou can remember their face,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.89,0:33:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们走路的姿势\Nand the way they move,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.02,0:33:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但却很难记得他们的声音\Nbut you can't hold on to the way they sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.35,0:33:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从未忘记过你的声音  父亲\NI never forgot your voice, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.23,0:33:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}宝贝\NSweetheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.46,0:33:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们没时间了\NWe're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.92,0:33:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以  你希望你父亲死在这里\NSo, this is where you wanted your father to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.74,0:33:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么回事  莎拉  他们是什么人\NWhat the hell, Sara, who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们是你女儿的同伴  兰斯警官\NAssociates of your daughter, Officer Kance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.09,0:33:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她交朋友的品味一向很差\NWell, she always did have the worst taste in friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.01,0:33:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真的以为我们找不到你吗\NDid you really think we weren't going to find you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.75,0:33:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然不会\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.31,0:33:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你们能找到\NI knew you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.49,0:33:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}动手\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.92,0:34:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你应该多注意周围的环境\NYou should be mindful of your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.65,0:34:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}枪是懦夫的武器\NGuns are a coward's weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.23,0:34:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有手枪你还会什么\NWhat are you without your side arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.20,0:34:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会拿出备用枪\NA guy with a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.45,0:34:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得  就因为你受宠\NYou think because you are the beloved
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.31,0:34:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就能得到自由吗\Nyou will be granted your freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.14,0:34:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}自由只有一种\NThere's only one freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.22,0:34:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我来赋予你自由\NLet me grant you yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不必做这么绝\NYou don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.83,0:35:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-都结束了  -还没\N- It's over! - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.75,0:35:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉  宝贝  不要\NSara, baby, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.46,0:35:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉拉尔斯・艾尔・古尔\NTell Ra's Al Ghul
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.88,0:35:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别惹我家人  有事冲着我来\Nthat my family is off limits. His quarrel is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.49,0:35:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉让你看到这些\NI'm sorry you saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不能想象你会怎么看待我\NI can't imagine what you must think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得你是幸存者\NI think you're a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.25,0:35:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是我见过的最勇敢的人\NI think you're one of the bravest people I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.70,0:35:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是我女儿\NYou're my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.76,0:35:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是时候回家了\NIt's time for you to come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.30,0:35:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我不能  -为什么\N- I can't  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.10,0:35:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们不会停止寻找我\NThey are never going to stop looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会保护你\NI'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.80,0:35:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会保护你\NWe'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-告诉她留下来是安全的  -爸爸\N- Tell her it's safe to stay.  - Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果他们伤害你  劳蕾尔或妈妈\NIf they hurt you or Laurel or mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.46,0:35:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那我也不活了\Nthen I really would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.86,0:35:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但她们应该知道你还活着\NBut they need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.29,0:35:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-不能告诉她们  爸爸  -为什么\N- They can't. They can't, daddy. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.19,0:36:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道原因  我回来是要确保家人安全\NYou know why! I came back to make sure that my family was safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们现在都没事\Nand you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.54,0:36:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但如果她们知道我还活着\NBut if they knew I was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}劳蕾尔和妈妈\NLaurel and mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.88,0:36:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她们会一直找我\Nthey would never stop looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.21,0:36:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这会令她们都丧命\Nand that could get them both killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.46,0:36:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不能放你走\NI can't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.82,0:36:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不能放你走\NI can't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.30,0:36:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我必须  爸爸  我必须走\NI have to--dad, I have to--I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.56,0:36:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}保护好他们\NKeep them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.38,0:36:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}探长\NDetective...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.72,0:36:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她说得对\NShe's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.92,0:36:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你必须为她保密\NYou have to keep her secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.42,0:36:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是我遇到的最难做到的事\NIt's already the hardest thing I've ever had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.90,0:37:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你都是怎么过这种日子的\NHow do you live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.32,0:37:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不介意孩子们来探视我\NI never mind getting a visit from my children,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.45,0:37:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我知道你们为什么而来\Nbut I know why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.46,0:37:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们只是想再说一件事\NWe just have one more thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.87,0:37:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}奥利弗  我们已经说好了\NOliver, we've already been through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.48,0:37:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会改变主意的\NI am not going to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.95,0:37:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这次是我改变主意\NThis is about me changing mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.98,0:37:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我觉得你不会想守着个秘密\NBecause I thought that you didn't want to go to trial over...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.57,0:37:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}受审\Na secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.79,0:37:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我遇上一个老朋友\NThen I caught up with an old friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.86,0:37:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看着她纠结于是否告诉家人她的秘密\Nand I watched as she struggled to tell her family hers,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.59,0:37:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为她担心\Nbecause she was afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.47,0:37:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}家人知道真相后会不再爱她\Nthat they wouldn't love her if they knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.26,0:37:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不论你担心的是什么\NWhatever you are worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.74,0:37:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都不会减弱我们对你的爱\Nit will not make us love you any less.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.80,0:37:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们不明白\NYou don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.86,0:37:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得你养育的是什么样的孩子\NWho do you think you raised?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.72,0:37:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你教会我们坚强\NYou taught us to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.49,0:37:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们可以战胜任何困难\NThat we could overcome any obstacle that we faced;
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.15,0:37:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}与之战斗\Nto fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你真的以为我们会轻易退缩吗\NDo you really think that we are going to scare that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.23,0:37:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不论发生什么\NWhatever comes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.65,0:38:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你都不会失去我们\Nyou won't lose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.88,0:38:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}永远不会\NEver.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.99,0:38:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会让简拒绝唐纳先生的辩诉交易\NI'll instruct Jean to reject Mr. Donner's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.02,0:38:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}爸爸\NDad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道我应该给你打电话\NI know I owe you a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有很多工作要做  我们能不能\NI have a lot of work. Can we--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.38,0:38:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们能不能下次再谈\Ncan we do this another time?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.40,0:38:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只想见见你  劳蕾尔\NI just had to see you, Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}发生了什么事吗  你还好吗\NDid something happen? Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.52,0:38:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总有一天  亲爱的\NOne day, honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.98,0:38:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当你有了自己的女儿\Nwhen you have a daughter of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.61,0:38:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你会理解为人父母\Nyou'll understand that being a parent,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.07,0:39:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}意味着你永远都在担心自己的孩子\Nit means you just never stop worrying about your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.69,0:39:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}爸爸  我很抱歉没有回你的电话\NDad, I'm--I'm sorry I didn't call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.46,0:39:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我\NI've--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.13,0:39:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这周过得很累\NI've had a really long week,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.40,0:39:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很累\NAnd--and I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.89,0:39:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还好吗\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.66,0:39:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望\NI wish that there was--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.88,0:39:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}发生一些事\Nthere was something, a...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.30,0:39:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}出现一切都好起来的迹象\Na sign that it gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.36,0:39:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会有的  亲爱的\NIt does, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.13,0:39:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会好起来的\NIt gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你怎么知道\NHow do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.06,0:39:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我希望我能告诉你  宝贝\NI wish I could tell you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.93,0:39:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也想告诉你\NI wish I could tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.98,0:39:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}莎拉去哪了\NWhere's Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.24,0:39:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她走了\NShe left.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.19,0:39:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们没什么吧\NYou cool with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.92,0:40:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没得选择\NI didn't have much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.32,0:40:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伏特加
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.51,0:40:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个老朋友给了我这个\NAn old friend gave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.19,0:40:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他说我会知道什么时候适合喝它\NSaid I would know when it was the right time to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.46,0:40:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在是合适的时候吗\NAnd now's the right time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不确定\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.16,0:40:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我要喝一杯\NBut I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.19,0:40:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}干杯\NProchnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.94,0:40:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这酒...\NHmm. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是对的\NSo you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.98,0:40:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我通常是对的  奥利弗\NYeah, I usually am, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么事  说真的\NAbout what, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}无论我多么努力  狄格尔  我的过去\NNo matter how hard I try, Diggle, my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.01,0:40:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}它并不想就此被掩埋\NIt doesn't want to stay buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想再努力尝试了\NI don't want to try so hard anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.57,0:41:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}过去我经历的五年里\NThe five years that I was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.04,0:41:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我并非一直待在岛上\NI wasn't always on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.83,0:41:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么是你\NHow are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.08,0:41:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}败寇没有发言权\NPrisoners do not speak.

